tle><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukayleighdrake.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KayleighDrake</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/16/02 9:53:41 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11084.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: TOFS Floor 8</span><hr size=1> You are wasting your time.<br><br>There is no 8th floor.<br><br>There is no 9th floor.<br><br>There is no secret/hidden floor. People have examined the zone file with things that show them the map of the entire zone - there are no hidden or unknown floors.<br><br>The highest floor, the one with the torches and the boss mob is all there is. Depending how you count, this could be called the 8th floor, but most people call it 7th (with 6th having two halves).<br><br>This comes up every month like clockwork. Repeat after me: There is no 8th floor.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unruter.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nruter</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/16/02 10:00:23 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11084.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: TOFS Floor 8</span><hr size=1> But how do you get to the 8th floor?<br><br>Nruter<br>L'il Assassin<br>Quellious-Ring Warden <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A 