h shadows<br>4. Sorcerous Bowl, identifies as: Item Lore: You feel an interference<br><br>ive tried giving Tserrina's Symbol to Cara Omica on 4th floor, no luck.<br><br>been thinking that possibly the Spirit Aids quest in Stonebrunt Mtns might have something to do with it.<br><br>perhaps if someone maxed their peacekeeper and kejek villager faction, a new quest would come up.<br><br>also, the harnassed soul gem is dropped by tserrina every single time. was thinking it might be able to be put through the same process as the crystallized shadow armor and weapons as well...might release something.<br><br>good luck all<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uaphyd.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aphyd</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/17/02 7:31:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11084.topic&index=9>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: mmm</span><hr size=1> The locked mirror on floor 7 leads to Iceclad.<br><br>Get a Guide to unlock it with their &quot;magic key&quot; some time..they pop up in IC. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=b1udragn>b1udragn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/18/02 8:53:40 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11084.topic&index=10>Reply</